data.title: Jandro
data.description: Waterproof, windproof and breathable vest in a combination of RPET materials, made from recycled plastic, to promote the reuse of plastic waste and contribute to the sustainability of the planet: 300g/m2 soft shell and elastane outside. with 100% polyester microfleece inside. Eco emblem on the bottom hem of the garment. With zipper closure and including chest and side pockets with invisible zip closure and matching pullers.  Available in a wide range of colours and in sizes S, M, L, XL, XXL.

data.title: Balmax
data.description: Waterproof and breathable waistcoat in combination of soft shell and elastane. In a wide range of bright tones, with zipper closure and front pockets. Available in sizes S, M, L, XL, XXL.

data.title: Tansy
data.description: Vest in warm and soft material, in combination of nylon and polyester. With recycled PET padding, zipper closure with strap in puller and large side pockets. Available in sizes M, L, XL, XXL.

data.title: Belsan
data.description: Vest in warm and soft, 100% polyester material. Extra lightweight material, water resistant and windbreaker, with inside padding. Zipper closure with strap in puller and large side pockets. Covered neck zipper and side pockets with pullers. Including a handy carrybag. Available in sizes S, M, L, XL, XXL.

data.title: Persol
data.description: Waterproof and breathable vest in soft shell 300g/m2. In an elegant two color design, with body in white color and details in grey. Zipper closure and front and side zipper pockets. Available in sizes S, M, L, XL, XXL.

data.title: Bordy
data.description: Waterproof and breathable vest in combination of soft shell and polyester materials.  In an elegant black color construction, with zipper closure and side zipper pockets, with pullers for easy opening. Available in sizes S, M, L, XL, XXL.

data.title: Rostol
data.description: Unisex vest in warm and soft material 100% polyester RPET, made from recycled plastic to encourage the reuse of plastic waste and contribute to the sustainability of the planet.   In extra light feather effect material, waterproof and windproof, with interior padding. Zippered neck with flap and puller strap, large zippered side pockets. RPET label and available in a wide range of colours. Sizes S, M, L, XL, XXL.

data.title: Kross
data.description: One of our top selling products in the Workwear Category, this high visibility reflective vest, compliant with all the relevant CE safety regulations, is a reliable choice especially if you work in the construction industry and want your employees to be always visible and safe. Bearing a double reflective strip around the body plus Velcro closures, this vest will make your team feel secure while promoting your brand�s identity and philosophy. One size fits all adults.

data.title: Forest
data.description: Waistcoat in warm and soft polar fleece of 280g/m2 with anti-pilling treatment. With colored inside collar, zipper closure with handle strap, side zipper pockets and elastic waist. Available in sizes M, L, XL, XXL.
